text: foreign
I'd like to share some important
learnings about human-centric data
management the foundation of what we can
call a novel data social contract for
the automotive industry
to start following other Industries such
as Banking and Healthcare the mobility
sector is the next area to undergo
digitization it requires specialization
to cleanse and unify huge volumes of
data
then remember what's in it for your
customers you need a clear value
proposition to justify the consent they
are giving you to use their data
finally it is undeniable that the new
Mobility ecosystem is emerging
more and more players are enabling this
transformation a magnitude not seen
since the days of the Model T
time to close up shop come by again
